OL,6,GWhat do viewers in Northern Ireland
OL,7,Gcall the third channel? ITV? ITV 1?
OL,8,GUTV? The UTV? Ulster Television?
OL,10,FThe name ITV plc thinks you should use
OL,11,Fis not at all clear even if the station
OL,12,Fbranding is now strong and explicit.
OL,14,FWith the revamp of ITV 1, visually
OL,15,FUTV's brand seems to have reached its
OL,16,Ffinal destination.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
OL,4,Csub-brand?
