OL,6,FTrails now follow the standard ITV 1
OL,7,Fformat. 1s fly over the screen as the
OL,8,Ftrail transitions to the endboard. Then
OL,9,Fat the very end the ITV 1 logo wipes
OL,10,Fon.
OL,12,FUTV is effectively a hallmark ` a
OL,13,Ftrusted brand which brings together the
OL,14,Flocal output.
OL,16,FVisually there is no doubt the channel
OL,17,Fname is ITV 1 ` trails, idents and the
OL,18,FDOG all highlight the name.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
