OL,6,FBefore it was just about conceivable
OL,7,Fthe ITV name (left out of local promos)
OL,8,Fwas just the old generic name for the
OL,9,Fnetwork.
OL,11,FBut orally the name is less clear.
OL,12,FAnnouncements before local programmes
OL,13,Frarely, if ever, give a name.
OL,15,FBut trails still tend to end with the
OL,16,Fwords "on UTV" ` even with the ITV 1
OL,17,Fname on screen.
OL,19,FSimilarly the EPG still refers solely
OL,20,Fto UTV.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
OL,4,Csub-brand?
