OL,6,FITV has always been very hesitant to be
OL,7,Fseen as downgrading the UTV brand. It
OL,8,Fis, of course, a name which goes back
OL,9,Fmany years.
OL,11,FBut we're at the point where the
OL,12,Fremaining hesitancy seems hard to
OL,13,Fjustify.
OL,15,FEven if there was a reluctance to
OL,16,Fexplicitly voice the name "ITV 1" on a
OL,17,Flocal trail, there are ways round this.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
OL,4,Csub-brand?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G4/8
