OL,6,FThe UTV Life trail points the way.
OL,7,FSimply don't say UTV as the channel
OL,8,Fname. Use the brand in other ways.
OL,9,FPerhaps in the title of the programme?
OL,10,FPerhaps by including a more subtle use
OL,11,Fof the name: "Join the UTV news team
OL,12,Ffor View from Stormont, Monday at
OL,13,F10.45pm."
OL,15,FThe other mystery concerns the EPG
OL,16,Fname.
OL,18,FIn English regions the name is simply
OL,19,F"ITV 1". Wales and the Scottish part of
OL,20,Fthe Border region are afforded an
OL,21,Fappropriate suffix.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
OL,4,Csub-brand?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G5/8
