OL,6,FBut the EPG name in Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fremains UTV alone.
OL,9,FTake one step back. This risks being
OL,10,Fconfusing to someone with no prior
OL,11,Fknowledge. Either the channel is ITV 1
OL,12,For UTV.
OL,14,FThe obvious thing to do is to change
OL,15,Fthe EPG name to "ITV 1 UTV"
OL,17,FNeither of these two changes would
OL,18,Fcause the sky to fall in but it would
OL,19,Fmake the channel name definitive.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
OL,4,Csub-brand?
