OL,6,FThe UTV name appears to have a future
OL,7,Fas a trusted sub-brand under the ITV 1
OL,8,Fmasterbrand. A hallmark on local
OL,9,Foutput.
OL,11,FI would be surprised if UTV Live does
OL,12,Fnot adopt explicit ITV News branding at
OL,13,Fsome point but I would also be shocked
OL,14,Fif the name changed unless there was a
OL,15,Fwider shake-up across the network. It's
OL,16,Fno "worse" than ITV News Granada
OL,17,FReports or ITV News Meridian.
